  <span id="freeText4038009556017513525" style="display:none">Deliciously, sumptuously detailed historical fiction, set mostly in 16th century Venice. It's all about whoredom and fine art. Throw in plenty of political corruption with a heavy salting of disease. Who could ask for more?</span>
