<div id="review_2683992134" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2683992134" />
    <a title="Lynn Horton" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/85322440-lynn-horton"><img alt="Lynn Horton" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1599505762p2/85322440.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2683992134?book_show_action=true">Jan 21, 2019</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Lynn Horton" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Lynn Horton" href="/user/show/85322440-lynn-horton">Lynn Horton</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="it was ok"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">it was ok</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2683992134" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer14812851672374337834">I seldom write two-star reviews, but at about the 30-percent mark, this story just wasn&apos;t worth my time anymore. It&apos;s crass, slow-moving, and just an ugly read. Yuck.</span>
  <span id="freeText14812851672374337834" style="display:none">I seldom write two-star reviews, but at about the 30-percent mark, this story just wasn't worth my time anymore. It's crass, slow-moving, and just an ugly read. Yuck.</span>
  <a data-text-id="14812851672374337834" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


