        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer1651848679" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer12006541856088935016">This is the second time that I have enjoyed a story by Dunant. This time, a risqué tale, narrated by the humorous dwarf Bucino of his ventures with his courtesan sidekick in 16th century Venice. A real treat to enjoy the last pages in the sunshine of an April day! </span>

          </span>
        </div>


